s in spending levels across the first weekend of the Games.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 430, \"end\": 435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999990482138, \"rank\": 9.517821474372847e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These included areas of commerce such as theatres & museums, food & grocery, restaurants, retail, and entertainment which boosted Paris' economy in that period.\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 681, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999990482138, \"rank\": 9.517821474372847e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Perfect Travel Companion  Owning a Visa card is like having a trusted travel companion by your side.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Visa card\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the key benefits that make your Visa card the perfect choice for a holiday abroad are:  \\u2022 Global Acceptance: Visa cards were accepted at millions of locations worldwide, making it easy to pay for goods and services no matter where you are.\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From dining at a quaint caf\\u00e9 in Paris to shopping at a bustling market in Tokyo, your Visa card ensures seamless transactions.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\