nts on travel-related expenses.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether it is a discount on hotel bookings, car rentals, or even flight tickets, Visa ensures the best deals, making holidays more affordable and enjoyable.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1662, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4732173910561893e-20, \"text\": \"Visa\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Visa_Inc.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ASUS Unveils Intel-Driven Copilot+ PCs at Always Incredible Media Day for IFA 2024  itel Energy launches revolutionary solar solutions, aiming to light up Nigerian homes, businesses  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1739, \"end\": 1743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ASUS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asus\"}, {\"begin\": 1894, \"end\": 1902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.9957996076081524, \"rank\": 0.004204159775387449, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}]}]}"